textAfterTable: Profile Artisan Mid Cap Fund is an open-end fund incorporated in the USA. The Fund's objective is maximum long-term capital growth. The Fund invests a portfolio of medium-sized US growth companies. The Fund invests in stocks of companies with franchise characteristics that are selling at attractive valuations and seem well positioned to take advantage of an accelerating profit cycle.
